Other third-party attributions
==============================================================================

ZolaOS uses many open-source libraries. The complete list of dependencies and
their respective licenses is maintained in THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md.

Notable upstream projects:
  - llama.cpp (MIT) — local LLM server with Vulkan/CUDA/Metal backends
  - PostgreSQL + pgvector (PostgreSQL License) — relational + vector storage
  - sentence-transformers (Apache 2.0) — bge-m3 embeddings runtime
  - FastAPI (MIT), Pydantic v2 (MIT), SQLAlchemy 2.0 (MIT) — application stack
  - structlog (Apache 2.0), OpenTelemetry (Apache 2.0) — observability
  - python-jose (MIT), bcrypt (Apache 2.0) — security primitives
  - openpyxl (MIT), python-docx (MIT), pypdf (BSD), Jinja2 (BSD) — documents

We thank these projects and their maintainers.
